            'partial scholarship' => 'Partial scholarships cover a portion of your education costs (25-75%), making them more accessible than full scholarships.\n\nCoverage:\nâ€¢ Tuition only: $5,000-$20,000/year\nâ€¢ Tuition + living: $10,000-$30,000/year\nâ€¢ Renewable annually based on performance\n\nEligibility:\nâ€¢ Good academic standing (GPA 3.0+)\nâ€¢ Financial need (for some programs)\nâ€¢ Field of study alignment\n\nStrategy: Combine multiple partial scholarships to cover significant costs. Many students receive 50-75% coverage through various awards.\n\nTips: Apply early, meet all deadlines, and don\'t limit yourself to one scholarship.',
